Package com.ezasm.assembler.parser

Class EzASMBaseListener

java.lang.Object
com.ezasm.assembler.parser.EzASMBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
EzASMListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
Assembler
public class EzASMBaseListener extends Object implements EzASMListener
This class provides an empty implementation of EzASMListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
